  {
    "content_id": 233560,
    "reference_id": 109198,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "列王紀下 8:16–10:36",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "12008016-12010036",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>約蘭和亞哈謝是南國的王，他們<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108206\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">娶了</span>亞哈家的女子。這些王遵循了亞哈邪惡的崇拜習俗。神向亞哈、<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108485\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">耶洗別</span>和亞哈的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108220\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">家族</span>施行了<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108233\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">審判</span>。神使用耶戶刑罰他們的邪惡行為和崇拜習俗。耶戶確保北國亞哈家的所有人都被殺死。他也確保所有支持亞哈的人都被殺死。這應驗了以利亞對亞哈所說的預言（列王紀上21:21–22）。耶戶也確保所有崇拜<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108401\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">巴力</span>的人都被殺死。這就是神如何停止暗利和亞哈的罪惡行為。那些王引導北國崇拜巴力而不是神。然而，耶戶並沒有忠心地跟隨神。他繼續犯耶羅波安拜<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108341\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">金牛犢</span>的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108195\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">罪</span>。</p>",
